snippet.title: FOX n FORESTS Prototype-Gameplay #1
snippet.description: This is our first gameplay video (without commentary;) from our prototype of FOX n FORESTS, featuring the level "Revolving River". If you like it, please check out our cool rewards on Kickstarter to make this 16-Bit dream come true: https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/foxnforests/fox-n-forests
